{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b9d16c28-b76f-4647-a304-9c0e99c62d1d","content":"**No — `net6.0` is not supported by MSTest v4.** \n\nMSTest 4.x dropped support for .NET 6.0 (it reached end-of-life in November 2024). The minimum supported target frameworks are:\n\n- **`net8.0`** (or later, e.g. `net9.0`)\n- **`net462`** (or later .NET Framework versions)\n\nYou'll need to update your `TargetFramework` to at least `net8.0`. For example:\n\n```xml\n<TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n```\n\nWould you like me to migrate your project to MSTest v4 with `net8.0`?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1dbc9821-c56c-476e-a3e0-a4c244d3186b","outputTokens":174,"requestId":"4C11:326A6D:36BBED:403C0C:6A0146C0"},"id":"dde08826-5683-4426-b305-c195a7e33b6b","timestamp":"2026-05-11T03:02:31.730Z","parentId":"89586c41-5b8a-4247-99e4-54fb39400408"}
